<div class="alert bg-gray  alert-dismissable hidden" id="helpBox">
    <button type="button" class="close" {{action 'hideHelp'}}>Ã—</button>
    <h4><i class="icon fa fa-info"></i> Help</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>Registration options are limited to what your attendee is eligible for based on age and gender.</li>
        <li>Use different Priorities to indicated how many weeks your camper wishes to attend and in which order to
            process your preferences.
        </li>
        <p>For example, to attend One session and indicate a second choice (in case your first choice is full), add
            another request with a
            priority of 2.</p>

        <p>To attend multiple weeks of camp, make more than one request <strong>with the same priority</strong>.</p>

        <p>Using the Priority field, you can construct your camper's summer plan just the way you want while adding
            backup options if your first choice isn't available.</p>
    </ul>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
        <div class="box">
            <div class="box-body">

                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <strong>Camper: </strong>{{registration.camper.firstName}} {{registration.camper.lastName}}
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <strong>Grade: </strong>
                        {{registration.camper.schoolGrade}}
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <strong>Gender: </strong> {{registration.camper.gender}}
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <dl class="">
                            <strong>Birthday: </strong>
                            {{moment registration.camper.dob 'MM/DD/YYYY'}}
                        </dl>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
            <!-- /.box-body -->
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
        <div class="box box-solid bg-yellow disabled">
            <div class="box-header">
                {{ fa-icon "calendar"}}
                <h3 class="box-title">Step 2: Request Specific Events To Attend</h3>
                <!-- tools box -->
                <div class="pull-right box-tools">
                    <!-- button with a dropdown -->
                    <div class="btn-group">
                        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" {{action "addRequest"}}>Add Request</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- /. tools -->
            </div>
            <!-- /.box-header -->
            <div class="box-body no-padding">
            </div>
            <!-- /.box-body -->
            <div class="box-footer text-black">

                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-md-2">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>Priority</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>Location</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>Session</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-3">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label>Program / Cabin</label>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="col-md-1">
                        <label>&nbsp;</label>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {{#each registration.requests as |item|}}
                    {{form-request request=item action="removeRequest" locations=locations sessions=sessions events=events mode=registration.mode}}
                {{/each}}
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>